    {
      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "The practical limit for most designs ended at 4 cores, with higher core count processors achieved with multi-chip modules and dual-core modules that shared and L2 cache and data fabric socket between core pairs. The crossbar wiring is usually done in the metal lines above the shared L3 caches, saving area. Intel’s 6-core Dunnington in 2008 used three dual-core modules with 16MB of shared L3.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0069",
      "parent_block_index": 69,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "The practical limit for most designs ended at 4 cores, with higher core count processors achieved with multi-chip modules and dual-core modules that shared and L2 cache and data fabric socket between core pairs. The crossbar wiring is usually done in the metal lines above the shared L3 caches, saving area. Intel’s 6-core Dunnington in 2008 used three dual-core modules with 16MB of shared L3.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "The practical limit for most designs ended at 4 cores, with higher core count processors achieved with multi-chip modules and dual-core modules that shared and L2 cache and data fabric socket between core pairs. The crossbar wiring is usually done in the metal lines above the shared L3 caches, saving area. Intel’s 6-core Dunnington in 2008 used three dual-core modules with 16MB of shared L3.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 394,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "大多数设计的实际极限止步于 4 个核心，核心数更高的处理器则是通过多芯片模块和双核模块来实现的，这些模块在核心对之间共享L2缓存与数据网络端口。交叉开关布线通常在共享L3缓存上方的金属层中完成，以节省面积。2008 年问世的英特尔 6 核 Dunnington 处理器便采用了三个双核模块，并配备 16MB 共享L3缓存。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-08T15:55:38.842909",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
